<h5 id="subject_485410">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=beafa1c534fcf9df69eac007353a5cfd&amp;topic=52638.msg485410#msg485410" rel="nofollow">[停坑合稿中]剑世界2.0 规则书1</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_485410'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_485410'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong> 于:</strong> 2012-11-02, 周五 02:08:17 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_485410_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
